Ariane Ascaride https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ariane_Ascaride 0 Ariane Ascaride (born 10 October 1954) is a French actress and screenwriter. She has appeared in films such as Marius et Jeannette (Marius and Jeannette), Ma vraie vie à Rouen (The True Story of My Life in Rouen; USA, My Life on Ice) and À la place du coeur (Where the Heart Is). She also starred in and co-wrote the screenplay for Le Voyage en Arménie (Armenia). Ariane_Ascaride ( born_10_October_1954 ) is a_French_actress_and_screenwriter .
